	<texts id="2001">
		<paragraph indent="0" tabs="" style="normal" height="0" width="400" y="+6" x="12" type="text">		<![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">It is very important to create a good impression with your final paragraph. The conclusion should be relevant to the arguments you have included in the main body of the composition and it should also give your opinion, with brief reasons for it.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
